sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent
    participant RLM as rlm-factory_query<br>(query_cache.py)
    participant VDB as vector-db_query<br>(query.py)
    participant Grep as Grep / Search Tools<br>(grep, find, rg)
    participant Ledger as RLM Ledger<br>(Markdown + YAML)
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB<br>(Vector Store)
    participant FileSys as File System

    Note over Agent, Ledger: Phase 1 -- RLM Summary Scan (Table of Contents)
    Note right of Agent: Pre-work: each file read ONCE,<br>summarized ONCE, cached forever.<br>Search summaries many times O(1).

    Agent->>RLM: "What does the vector query tool do?"
    RLM->>Ledger: Key/Value lookup across all summaries
    Ledger-->>RLM: 1-sentence dense summary per file

    alt Phase 1 Sufficient -- summary answers the question
        RLM-->>Agent: Return matching summary + file path
        Agent->>Agent: Proceed with high-level understanding
        Note right of Agent: "I have enough context to continue."
    else Phase 1 Insufficient -- need to locate exact content
        Note over Agent, Chroma: Phase 2 -- Vector DB Semantic Search (Back-of-Book Index)
        Agent->>VDB: "Find exact code for vector semantic search"
        VDB->>Chroma: Nearest-neighbor embedding search
        Chroma-->>VDB: Ranked parent chunks + RLM Super-RAG context
        VDB-->>Agent: Returns specific file snippets with source paths

        alt Phase 2 Sufficient -- chunk contains the answer
            Agent->>Agent: Perform deep analysis on returned chunks
            Note right of Agent: "Found the exact context needed."
        else Phase 2 Insufficient -- need exact keyword or line
            Note over Agent, FileSys: Phase 3 -- Grep / Exact Search (Ctrl+F)
            Agent->>Grep: Search for specific keyword, symbol, or pattern
            Grep->>FileSys: rg / grep across discovered file paths
            FileSys-->>Grep: Exact matching lines + line numbers
            Grep-->>Agent: Precise location of specific text
            Agent->>Agent: Read targeted file section
        end
    end

